# New Ticket (Analyse)

The user can create ticket for a selected report.  

---

![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)





![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)

To finish their ticket they have to answer the all following questions.
![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)

The user can update the name or description of the ticket or invite someone to answer questions.
![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)


When a user is invited, a page like the one below will open without having to log in. The user is expected to answer all questions.
![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)


When the user answers all the questions, the ticket close button will be active. When the user close this case, the user will get contacted by support within 1 day. The user can give feedback after the ticket is closed.

![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)



The user can review and rating the ticket.
![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)
